# YouTrack REST API Skill

Use the YouTrack REST API via `curl` for ALL YouTrack operations. Do NOT use YouTrack MCP tools.

## Auth & Base URL

```bash
YT_AUTH=$(python3 -c "import json; print(json.load(open('$HOME/.claude.json'))['mcpServers']['youtrack']['headers']['Authorization'])")
YT_BASE="{{YOUTRACK_API_BASE}}"
```

All `curl` calls below assume: `curl -s --max-time 10 -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH"`

## Issues

```bash
# Search issues
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" "$YT_BASE/issues?fields=id,summary,project(shortName),customFields(name,value(name))&query=project:{{YOUTRACK_PROJECT_CODE}}+%23Unresolved"

# Get single issue (full details)
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" "$YT_BASE/issues/{{YOUTRACK_PROJECT_CODE}}-172?fields=id,summary,description,project(shortName),reporter(login),customFields(name,value(name)),links(direction,linkType(name),issues(id,summary))"

# Create issue
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  "$YT_BASE/issues?fields=id,idReadable" \
  -d '{"project":{"id":"0-3"},"summary":"Title","description":"Body","customFields":[{"name":"Type","$type":"SingleEnumIssueCustomField","value":{"name":"Task"}},{"name":"Priority","$type":"SingleEnumIssueCustomField","value":{"name":"Normal"}}]}'

# Create subtask (link as parent)
# First create issue, then link:
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  "$YT_BASE/issues/{{YOUTRACK_PROJECT_CODE}}-NEW/links" \
  -d '{"direction":"OUTWARD","linkType":{"name":"Subtask"},"issues":[{"id":"{{YOUTRACK_PROJECT_CODE}}-172"}]}'

# Update issue
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  "$YT_BASE/issues/{{YOUTRACK_PROJECT_CODE}}-172" -X POST \
  -d '{"summary":"New title","description":"New desc","customFields":[{"name":"State","$type":"StateIssueCustomField","value":{"name":"In Progress"}}]}'

# Add comment
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  "$YT_BASE/issues/{{YOUTRACK_PROJECT_CODE}}-172/comments" \
  -d '{"text":"Comment in **markdown**"}'

# Attach file
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" \
  -F "file=@/path/to/file.pdf" \
  "$YT_BASE/issues/{{YOUTRACK_PROJECT_CODE}}-172/attachments?fields=id,name"

# Log work
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  "$YT_BASE/issues/{{YOUTRACK_PROJECT_CODE}}-172/timeTracking/workItems" \
  -d '{"duration":{"minutes":30},"text":"Description","type":{"name":"Development"}}'
```

## Knowledge Base Articles

```bash
# List articles
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" "$YT_BASE/articles?fields=id,summary,project(shortName)&\$top=20"

# Get article content
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" "$YT_BASE/articles/ARTICLE-ID?fields=id,summary,content,project(shortName)"

# Create article
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  "$YT_BASE/articles?fields=id,idReadable,summary" \
  -d '{"project":{"id":"0-3"},"summary":"Article Title","content":"Article body in **markdown**"}'

# Update article
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  "$YT_BASE/articles/ARTICLE-ID" -X POST \
  -d '{"summary":"Updated title","content":"Updated content"}'

# Attach file to article
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" \
  -F "file=@/path/to/file.pdf" \
  "$YT_BASE/articles/ARTICLE-ID/attachments?fields=id,name"
```

## Project Info

```bash
# List projects
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" "$YT_BASE/admin/projects?fields=id,shortName,name&\$top=50"

# Get project details (custom fields schema, work types)
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" "$YT_BASE/admin/projects/0-3?fields=id,shortName,name,customFields(field(name),bundle(values(name)))"

# Get field schema for issue creation
curl -s -H "Authorization: $YT_AUTH" "$YT_BASE/admin/projects/0-3/customFields?fields=field(name),bundle(values(name)),canBeEmpty,emptyFieldText"
```

## Common Field Types for customFields

| Field | `$type` |
|-------|---------|
| Type, Priority, State | `SingleEnumIssueCustomField` |
| Assignee | `SingleUserIssueCustomField` (value: `{"login":"REDACTED_USER"}`) |
| Due Date | `DateIssueCustomField` (value: epoch ms) |
| Estimation | `PeriodIssueCustomField` (value: `{"minutes":120}`) |

## Tips

- Always use `fields=` parameter to limit response size
- Use `$top` and `$skip` for pagination
- Query syntax: `project:{{YOUTRACK_PROJECT_CODE}} #Unresolved for:me State:{In Progress}`
- API docs: https://www.jetbrains.com/help/youtrack/devportal/youtrack-rest-api.html
